Method Detail

resumeTraversal

public com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.DocumentList resumeTraversal(java.lang.String checkpoint)
                                                                 throws com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.RepositoryException
Starts the traversal from a checkpoint specified by CM. The connector has returned this checkpoint information to the CM at the completion of last vtraversal. Though, SharePoint Connector does not really make use of this checkpoint information for resuming the travesal. Instead, it uses the state file for this purpose. State file implementation is specific to the connector and CM is unaware of this.

Specified by:
resumeTraversal in interface com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.TraversalManager
Parameters:
checkpoint - Not really used by the SharePoint connector

com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.RepositoryException
